text: I Quit smoking 5 years ago and started vaping. I asked my sister for her opinion as to whom I should purchase my eliquid from. She without hesitation said, "Buy from totally wicked.com.". I tried them out and have purchased every drop of eliquid I have used ever since. I get my orders very quickly typically in two business days. I have screwed my order up and emailed them with my errors. They fixed my order and I still got it in two days. They have great sales and "I love these people". Buy your vaping supplies from Totally Wicked.Com.
